location.fullValue: Cashman Plan, Summit at Northpointe at Vistancia

data.description: Beautiful TW Lewis-built luxury home in a gated community w/ spectacular mountain views! Enter the private & paved courtyard that is perfect for a morning cup of coffee. As you enter the spacious entry, take notice of the crown molding & wood shutters throughout. Plenty of room for guests w/ 3 extra bedrooms & complementing baths. The open kitchen is adjacent to the family room & is great for entertaining. It offers a large island, eating nook, double ovens, 5 burner gas cooktop, RO & conveying fridge. The oversized owners suite features a large walk-in closet, soaking tub, walk-in shower, double high sinks & private exit to the back patio. Welcome to your backyard paradise! Open up the multi-panel family room slider to the covered travertine patio. The gas heated pool, BBQ island & fire pit make this perfect for entertaining & enjoying the spectacular mountain views. New hard PVC irrigation piping w/ new valves & timers were installed last year. The garage has 3 stalls w/ plenty of room for storage & a new water heater & water softener. This home is efficient w/ a new 18 seer AC unit, new furnace & Wifi controlled thermostats. You can expect lower electric bills w/ the solar system. Includes a whole-home fire sprinkler system. The community of Vistancia is a full master-planned development that includes beautiful homes, parks & hiking trails throughout, award winning community center & golf courses, commercial & retail shops, and incredible desert landscape all around! Vistancia has ranked as the #1 Master Planned Community in AZ for the 10th year in a row (2014-2023)! Come & see why!
